    },
    {
      "id": "el_5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 125,
      "width": 344,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Amount:  A = P × (1 + R/100)^T\nCompound Interest:  CI = A - P\n\nHalf-yearly:  A = P × (1 + R/200)^(2T)\nQuarterly:    A = P × (1 + R/400)^(4T)\n\nWHY: Each year, interest earns interest too.\n  Year1: P×(1+R/100)\n  Year2: P×(1+R/100)² ...and so on\n\nEx: P=1000, R=10%, T=2yr\n  A=1000×1.1²=1210, CI=210",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 5,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f0"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Amount:  A = P × (1 + R/100)^T\nCompound Interest:  CI = A - P\n\nHalf-yearly:  A = P × (1 + R/200)^(2T)\nQuarterly:    A = P × (1 + R/400)^(4T)\n\nWHY: Each year, interest earns interest too.\n  Year1: P×(1+R/100)\n  Year2: P×(1+R/100)² ...and so on\n\nEx: P=1000, R=10%, T=2yr\n  A=1000×1.1²=1210, CI=210",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
