    {
      "id": "el_23",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 766,
      "width": 332,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: P=10000, R=10%, T=3\nStep 2: A = 10000×(1.1)³ = 10000×1.331\n  = 13310, CI = 13310-10000 = 3310\n\nTRICK:\nYear-by-year: 10000→11000→12100→13310\nCI each yr: 1000, 1100, 1210\n(each yr = prev + 10% of prev)\n\n  10000─[+10%]→11000─[+10%]→12100─[+10%]→13310\n\nAnswer: CI = Rs.3310 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
