    {
      "id": "el_43",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1163,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: CI = P×[(1.05)²-1]\n  1025 = P×[1.1025-1]\n  1025 = P×0.1025\nStep 2: P = 1025/0.1025 = 10000\n\n  P=? ──[5%]──→ Yr1 ──[5%]──→ Yr2\n  CI=1025 → P=10000\n  10000─→10500─→11025 (CI=1025) ✓\n\nTRICK:\nCI = P×[(1+R/100)^T - 1]\nP = CI / [(1+R/100)^T - 1]\n= 1025/0.1025 = 10000\n\nAnswer: P = Rs.10000 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
