    {
      "id": "el_48",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1163,
      "width": 231,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: (1+R/100)² = 13520/12500\n  = 1.0816\nStep 2: 1+R/100 = √1.0816 = 1.04\n  R = 4%\n\nTRICK:\nA/P = 1.0816 → recognize (1.04)²\nMemorize: (1.04)²=1.0816\n(1.05)²=1.1025 (1.10)²=1.21\n\n  12500─[?%]→13000─[?%]→13520\n\nAnswer: R = 4% ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
