    {
      "id": "el_53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1605,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: (1.1)^T = 4840/4000 = 1.21\nStep 2: Try powers of 1.1:\n  (1.1)¹=1.1  (1.1)²=1.21 ← match!\n  T = 2 years\n\nTRICK:\nA/P = 121/100 = (11/10)²\nExponent = 2 → T = 2\n\n  4000─[10%]→4400─[10%]→4840\n\nAnswer: T = 2 years ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
