      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: (1.1)^T = 4840/4000 = 1.21\nStep 2: Try powers of 1.1:\n  (1.1)¹=1.1  (1.1)²=1.21 ← match!\n  T = 2 years\n\nTRICK:\nA/P = 121/100 = (11/10)²\nExponent = 2 → T = 2\n\n  4000─[10%]→4400─[10%]→4840\n\nAnswer: T = 2 years ✓",
