      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1621,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Rate/period = 5%, Periods = 3\nStep 2: A = 20000×(1.05)³\n  = 20000×1.157625 = 23152.50\n  CI = 3152.50\n\nTRICK:\nHalf-yearly: R→R/2, T→2T\n10%/2=5% per half, 1.5yr=3 halves\n20000─[5%]→21000─[5%]→22050─[5%]→23152.50\n\nAnswer: CI = Rs.3152.50 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
