      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Rate/period = 5%, Periods = 3\nStep 2: A = 20000×(1.05)³\n  = 20000×1.157625 = 23152.50\n  CI = 3152.50\n\nTRICK:\nHalf-yearly: R→R/2, T→2T\n10%/2=5% per half, 1.5yr=3 halves\n20000─[5%]→21000─[5%]→22050─[5%]→23152.50\n\nAnswer: CI = Rs.3152.50 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
