      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Rate/qtr = 5%, Periods = 3\nStep 2: A = 16000×(1.05)³\n  = 16000×1.157625 = 18522\n  CI = 2522\n\nTRICK:\nQuarterly: R→R/4, T→4T\n20%/4=5% per qtr, 9mo=3 quarters\n16000─[5%]→16800─[5%]→17640─[5%]→18522\n\nAnswer: CI = Rs.2522 ✓",
