    {
      "id": "el_68",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1976,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Different rates each year\nStep 2: A = P×(1.10)×(1.15)×(1.20)\n  = 200000×1.518 = 303600\n\nTRICK:\nChain multiply: just cascade!\n200000→220000→253000→303600\n(×1.10, ×1.15, ×1.20)\n\n  200000─[+10%]→220000─[+15%]→253000─[+20%]→303600\n\nAnswer: Population = 303600 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
