      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Different rates each year\nStep 2: A = P×(1.10)×(1.15)×(1.20)\n  = 200000×1.518 = 303600\n\nTRICK:\nChain multiply: just cascade!\n200000→220000→253000→303600\n(×1.10, ×1.15, ×1.20)\n\n  200000─[+10%]→220000─[+15%]→253000─[+20%]→303600\n\nAnswer: Population = 303600 ✓",
