    {
      "id": "el_73",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1960,
      "width": 346,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: V = P×(1-R/100)^T\n  = 150000×(0.80)³\nStep 2: = 150000×0.512 = 76800\n\nTRICK:\nMemorize: (0.80)³ = 0.512\n150000×0.512 = 76800\nTRAP: 20%×3=60%? NO! Actual=48.8%\n\n  150000─[-20%]→120000─[-20%]→96000─[-20%]→76800\n\nAnswer: Value = Rs.76800 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
