    {
      "id": "el_78",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1960,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: X/(1.1) + X/(1.1)² = 2000\n  X/1.1 + X/1.21 = 2000\nStep 2: 1.1X + X = 2420\n  2.1X = 2420 → X = 1152.38\n\n  2000 ──→ Pay X/(1.1) + X/(1.1)² = 2000\n  Yr1: pay 1152.38 | Yr2: pay 1152.38\n\nTRICK:\nEMI = P×r×(1+r)^n / [(1+r)^n - 1]\n= 2000×0.1×1.21 / 0.21\n= 242/0.21 = 1152.38\n\nAnswer: Installment = Rs.1152.38 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
