      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: X/(1.1) + X/(1.1)² = 2000\n  X/1.1 + X/1.21 = 2000\nStep 2: 1.1X + X = 2420\n  2.1X = 2420 → X = 1152.38\n\n  2000 ──→ Pay X/(1.1) + X/(1.1)² = 2000\n  Yr1: pay 1152.38 | Yr2: pay 1152.38\n\nTRICK:\nEMI = P×r×(1+r)^n / [(1+r)^n - 1]\n= 2000×0.1×1.21 / 0.21\n= 242/0.21 = 1152.38\n\nAnswer: Installment = Rs.1152.38 ✓",
