    {
      "id": "el_83",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2326,
      "width": 353,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: (1+R/100)^8 = 2\n  1+R/100 = 2^(1/8) = 1.0905\nStep 2: R = 9.05%\n\n  |█| → |██| (2× in 8yr)\n  → |████| (4× in 16yr) → |████████| (8× in 24yr)\n\nTRICK:\nRule of 72: R = 72/T\n= 72/8 = 9% (close to exact 9.05%)\n\n  6%→12yr  10%→7.2yr  12%→6yr\n  2× in n yrs → 4× in 2n → 8× in 3n\n\nAnswer: R ≈ 9% ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
