    {
      "id": "el_88",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2342,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: E = (1+R/(n×100))^n - 1\n  = (1+10/200)² - 1\nStep 2: = (1.05)² - 1 = 0.1025 = 10.25%\n\n  Nominal 10%: H1=5% | H2=5%\n  100─[+5%]→105─[+5%]→110.25\n  Effective = 10.25% > Nominal 10%\n\nTRICK:\nFor half-yearly at R%:\nE = R + (R/2)²/100\n= 10 + 25/100 = 10.25%\nMore frequent → higher effective rate\n\nAnswer: Effective Rate = 10.25% ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 8800,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 88,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_14"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: E = (1+R/(n×100))^n - 1\n  = (1+10/200)² - 1\nStep 2: = (1.05)² - 1 = 0.1025 = 10.25%\n\n  Nominal 10%: H1=5% | H2=5%\n  100─[+5%]→105─[+5%]→110.25\n  Effective = 10.25% > Nominal 10%\n\nTRICK:\nFor half-yearly at R%:\nE = R + (R/2)²/100\n= 10 + 25/100 = 10.25%\nMore frequent → higher effective rate\n\nAnswer: Effective Rate = 10.25% ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
