    {
      "id": "el_93",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2342,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A = P×(1.04)×(1.05)×(1.06)\nStep 2: 25000→26000→27300→28938\n  CI = 28938-25000 = 3938\n\nTRICK:\nChain multiply step by step:\n25000×1.04=26000\n26000×1.05=27300\n27300×1.06=28938\nNote: order doesn't matter!\n\nAnswer: CI = Rs.3938 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
